PrecisAuthority for the VANCOUVER PORT CORPORATION to enter into a real estate transaction with CANADIAN PACIFIC LIMITED whereby VPC will acquire title to one strip of land (3,780 m²), and IN EXCHANGE, C.P. will acquire title to three parcels of land (2,399m²) encumbered by an easement in perpetuity in favour of VPC, all of them being situated on the south shore of Burrard Inlet.
